<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>MNNIT Community</title>

  <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/style.css">

</head>
<body>

  <header class="jumbotron">
    <img src="images/mnnit.png" alt="mnnit">
    <h1 class="display-3">MNNIT Community</h1>
    <p class="lead">Revitalizing College Activities for a Galactic Experience</p>
  </header>

  <div class="container">
    <section>
      <h2>About Us</h2>
      <p>
        Welcome to the MNNIT Community – where we're on a mission to bring life back into the college activities scene!
        Sadly, our clubs have been a bit quiet lately, and we're here to change that. Join us in making college life more vibrant and engaging.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section class="what-doing">
      <h2>What we will be doing?</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Community Bonding:</strong> Unite with fellow MNNITians to learn, share projects, and build a close-knit community.</li>
        <li><strong>Weekly Newsletter:</strong> Stay tuned for our MNNIT weekly newsletter! <a target="_blank" href="https://forms.gle/4ZaKsHSht4SNg1TT7">Apply to be a writer</a>.</li>
    <li><strong>Talent Showcase:</strong> Highlight your diverse talents—poetry, music, acting, sports, programming, and more!</li>
    <li><strong>Exciting Events:</strong> Join thrilling competitions and engaging events that bring out the best in everyone.</li>
    <li><strong>And More Surprises:</strong> Brace yourself for collaborations and surprises as we embark on this exciting journey together!</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section text-center">
      <h2 class="mb-4 cta-text">Ready to Join the Fun?</h2>
      <a href="https://discord.gg/7M47mysQzH" class="btn discord-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Join Our Discord Server</a>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Get Involved</h2>
      <p>
        We encourage you to take an active part in our weekly newsletters, talent showcases, and club activities.
        Let's make our college experience unforgettable together!
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>

  <!-- Bootstrap JS (optional, for some components) -->
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
